message:
US State Department spokesman Crowley says Washington eyes Iranian warships in Mediterranean.

‎"Two Iranian vessels are docking at Syria port after they passed through the Suez Canal for the first time since the victory of the Islamic Revolution in Iran.... An Iranian diplomat... said... that these vessels are heading to Syria for training & Iran's request for passage through the Suez Canal is 'within international law.'"
